data.description:
Welcome to 1037 Timber Gap Crossing! This stunning home is located in the desirable community of Breckenridge, known for its peaceful surroundings and family-friendly environment. This immaculate home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and an open concept living area perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet night in.

As you step inside, you will be greeted by a beautiful foyer that leads to the inviting living room with a cozy fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage. The breakfast nook is perfect for enjoying a cup of coffee in the morning or a quick snack in the afternoon.

The master suite is a true oasis, featuring a large bedroom with a walk-in closet and a spa-like master bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower. The three additional bedrooms are spacious and perfect for a growing family or guests. The backyard is a private retreat, with a covered patio and plenty of room for outdoor activities.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home. Schedule a showing today!
